{
  "stem": "22979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't tell you the sum because I [? didn't ?] [? know. ?] And I didn't know-- I-- I don't know even the family in lager.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, we had a very good friend, Erik Kolka, who in 1968, from Prague, went to-- he worked with me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He worked in the book business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a manager for 15 years in the largest military bookstore in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was in Prague.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we met many times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was also in Auschwitz a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was in Auschwitz to repair, you know, like a mechanic, a plumber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- he came very often to the working place where I working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, you know, we exchange a few words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the war, we met.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since '68, he went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was working at a Hebrew university in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from Jerusalem, he visited us in-- in America quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, he got an honorary doctor degree from the-- from the Chicago University.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can we go back to Birkenau and the gypsies?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Had you any personal contact with gypsies at all?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the gypsies-- no, I didn't-- because they were always separated, since they start bringing them in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although, we had, in Birkenau, also lesbians-- I [? can ?] say homosexuals because I was in [INAUDIBLE], which I knew from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's still alive and very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whenever we are in Bratislava, we visit her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a physician in Auschwitz too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Muncie ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Schwalbova. ?] And I know one Reichsdeutsche [? politzche ?] with whom she was very good friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was rumors that they were lesbians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then I know kapos-- the German kapos-- which were also rumors.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
